title: STOP IN TO SEE OUR BEAUTIFUL COMMUNITY!!!
posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', 'Carrington Park at Gulf Pointe boasts one of the most prominent locations on the outer loop, with great proximity to access I-45 and Beltway 8.', 'The location at our Houston area apartments allows you to enjoy unmatched convenience to Downtown, NASA’s Johnson Space Center, Houston’s Hobby Airport, and the most elite shopping and dining that Houston has to offer.', ' Our Apartments in Houston, TX have more than just location to offer.', 'Take a look at our property amenities including a resort-style pool with Wi-Fi, gourmet grilling areas, a billiards room and more.', 'Contact us to find out how to make Carrington Park at Gulf Pointe the place you will be proud to call home!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Billiards Room', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Intrusion Alarms', 'High-End Appliances', 'Pets Welcome', 'Enjoy our Partnership with Comcast Cable', 'Business Center with High Speed Internet Access', 'Private Patio or Balcony', 'Full Size Washer & Dryer', 'In Each Apartment Home', 'Ceiling Fans in Living Room & Master Bedroom', 'Built-in Computer Desks', 'Attached Garages with Individual Driveway and Private Entry', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
